Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H262B96&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara had completed blueprints for GOD's\NRS Device, which can convert any matter into energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling the RS Device should benefit mankind, Nanbara tore\Nthe blueprints up and sent eight pieces to old colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The ninth and final piece was hidden\Nin his daughter Rie's pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrusting the blueprints' safety to the\NX Rider, Dr. Nanbara left this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Vengeful Ogre Geronimo! Silent Assault!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those blueprints are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The names of those eight colleagues\Nare bound to be in here. Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time looking\Nfor a list of those names!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I already looked; Dr. Nanbara's too cautious\Nto leave something like that lying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'd fall for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,More likely you already stole the list yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed many white men after their\Nlies turned me into a vengeful ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood of the great Indian leader\NGeronimo flows within me! Get him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you you're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the X Rider go? Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He already beat them...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about finding those\Nblueprints, Scorpion Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Blasted GOD monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Still nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... No sign of anyone that was\Nworking with the doctor before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even one clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just eight people in all of Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your rice balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Ok, did I forget anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-You just be careful!\N-Climbing the Tanzawas is like hiking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, my friends are basically veterans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make a schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, first up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shou, what's this drawing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it in a letter for dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks important! What if you'd lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm keeping it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I can't find the blueprints...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Morning!\N-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where's Mako?\N-Sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As if! She hasn't even had\Na cold since she was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-So, she's playing hooky!\N-No, she's visiting her grandpa's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Visiting a grave...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Here lies Nanbara Kouichi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara, I was shocked\Nto get your letter to father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... afraid he died in a\Ntraffic accident last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But please don't worry. My brother\Nand I will protect that blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-I've brought you some water...\N-Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be a kind young lady,\Nvisiting a grave at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how my father raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard this man was a great doctor...\NWas your father a scientist also?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll get some clues here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't see any hint of GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that girl has one of the blueprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but did you know Dr. Nanbara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And your father was a scientist too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Might I know why you're asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara gave me a job\Nto do. I can't fail him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... in a hurry. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...Guess it's too soon for her to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...Or did I imagine it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke... So you're keeping\Nan eye on his grave too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... the priest from the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you didn't make a donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I forgot! What can I give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The piece of paper you received from Dr. Nanbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, but that's--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be coy. I know all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:09:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was Dr. Yazawa, Dr. Nanbara's\Nclosest friend amongst his eight colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then someone is after the blueprint he sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes; me. Scorpion Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your piece of the blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stubborn girl, don't you\Nwant to live? Talk! Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A scorpion...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to die for a piece of\Npaper that has nothing to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara entrusted it to us... We have to protect it, for mankind's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I shan't give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better talk! Unless you want\Nto be stung to death by my scorpion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpion Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Clever move, disguising yourself as a priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run, Scorpion Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! You're the one who should\Nbe running, X Rider! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, do you want this girl to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No one asked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Report this to King Dark: The second piece\Nof the blueprints belongs to the X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up so easily! I'll get it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like watching the doctor's grave paid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm the one you should be\Nthanking for giving you that hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because I brought it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, will you trust me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sure she will!\N-Sure she will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you two keep it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... where's the blueprint\NDr. Nanbara sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My little brother Shouichi has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And where's Shouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He went hiking in the Tanzawas this mor--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A spy scorpion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpion Geronimo heard\Neverything we just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And my brother? What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to bring him back safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Shouichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's take a little\Nbreak. Have a seat, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost looks like Native\NAmerican smoke signals...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Native Americans!\N-Native Americans?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of you is Yazawa\NShouichi? Talk! Out with it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with Yazawa?\NWho are you people!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yazawa Shouichi!\NWhy are you doing this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Yazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright Shouichi, give me\Nthat blueprint of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Blueprint? I don't know\Nwhat you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister Keiko told me!\NDon't try to hide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-My sister...?\N-So give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you'll hand it over? A second\Nvolley will be the end of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yazawa, you have to give it to\Nthem, no matter how precious it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sir!\N-Alright, I'll do it for you guys... I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here!\N-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouichi, you don't need to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider! Fire,\Nfire! Slaughter them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mountain hut nearby,\Nsir. Can you take them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Alright! Let's go!\N-Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Everyone alright?\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sir, Sawai's not here!\N-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll have to find\Nhim. You all wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have died if I stayed\Nwith Yazawa... No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? You don't want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad pair of hostages!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go look for him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-C'mon!!\N-Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kids alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Sawai went missing,\Nso sir's looking for him, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:17:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, X Rider! I've got\Nthe kid and his teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Save us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy isn't Yazawa\NShouichi! Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, my only objective\Nis Dr. Nanbara's blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me, or I'll kill\Nthe boy and his teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll count to five. Bring\Nout the blueprints or they die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die! Please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's five!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me instead if you have\Nto! I've got the blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, bring that blueprint to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll do anything to achieve his goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a brave boy, but we've\Ngot no choice but to hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to bring it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpion Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the second piece of the blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Release Sawai and his teacher first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've earned Scorpion\NGeronimo's trust, X Rider. Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Go on, quickly.\N-Right. Come on, inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'll have your piece too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This strategy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice-spouting wimps like you can't\Nstand to see innocents die, can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just work that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rider!\N-Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it! That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-X!\N-Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, the second blueprint piece is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Rhino Beetle Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the third piece of the blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the X Rider and King Dark have\None piece of the RS Device's blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But where are the remaining seven pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A scientist uses a special light ray to tattoo\Ntwo boys' backs with the third blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Learning this, GOD's Rhino Beetle\NLupin pursues the boys to retrieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Mysterious Phantom Thief Rhino Beetle Lupin!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider